      <description>&lt;figure&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;https://engsner.com/images/collinear-robot/collinear-robot.jpg&#34;
         alt=&#34;The robot balancing on a wooden floor&#34;/&gt; &lt;figcaption&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;The robot in action&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a capstone project (Gymnasiearbete), I was one in a group of three who built a balancing robot.
I was responsible for writing the code. This entailed making an estimate of the current angle,
interacting with a PID controller, communicating with the motor controllers,
as well as allowing manual control through a Playstation 4 controller.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The code is available on &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Sunkworks/Colinear-Balance-Bot&#34;&gt;Github&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
